    "intent": "Single-select segmented control. Compound API: root manages selection state (controlled via `value` or uncontrolled via `defaultValue`) and track paint; `SegmentedControl.Item` renders each segment with optional icon/CounterBadge slots. `attention` drives selected-segment prominence (bold/subtle), `trackEmphasis` drives the track container prominence, `shape` is pill or rectangular, `type` is text or icon-only."
